<p>C++</p>

<p>C++ is a high-performance, object-oriented programming language used for developing system software, gaming, and high-performance applications. It offers efficient memory management and low-level control, making it ideal for building performance-critical software solutions.</p>
<h4>Features:</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Efficient memory management</li>
    <li>Low-level control</li>
    <li>Object-oriented programming</li>
    <li>Templates and generic programming</li>
    <li>Rich standard library</li>
</ul>